clusterList.phrase: i have long stopped worrying about what is realist and what is not mohamed abu soweilim the main character in the land falling down at the end of the film while being dragged to his death by soldiers on horseback is a realist enough gesture but for him to plough the land with his bleeding fingers as he dies is not when i thought about this i realised that it didn't bother me whether the two gestures were realist or not i just went ahead and filmed them
